snippet.title: Atomic Shrimp
snippet.description:
Atomic Shrimp is about ideas.  Ideas that lead to crafts, inventions and recipes, investigations, new skills, and the general appreciation of being alive.

It's also about looking at the world with curiosity and wonder, appreciating the small things, loving the underdog and embracing new things at the same time as cherishing older traditions, or sometimes turning them upside down.

Follow me on Instagram for sneak previews of upcoming projects and other content
